data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home. Two story with a loft that would be great for an office or extra living area. Spacious primary bedroom with walk-in closet conveniently located downstairs. Primary bathroom has dual sink, jetted tub & separate shower. Freshly painted & laminate wood floors just installed.  Corner lot with large yard, has lots of potential.  Seller willing to help with up to $3000.00 for buyer's closing costs.
